    "Special attention needs to be paid to the organization of an effective system of support for veterans of the Russian-Ukrainian war (Lashko et al., 2023).",
    "Full mobilization of the efforts of state bodies, doctors, psychologists, and volunteers is necessary to solve them.",
    "It will probably not do without the support of foreign partners, first of all their practical experience (Matiashova, Tsagkaris, Essar, Romash, Vus, 2022).",
